{"tid":2217207,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【去中國化】中華鳥會遭國際鳥盟除名 英文名索性從「Chinese」改為「Taiwan」","createTime":"2020-09-25T09:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T09:26:35.000Z","uid":2054,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5161ca20d4391e352892a023c5f63b8941ba2c7e","tid":2217207,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T09:23:55.000Z","msg":"自由時報全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3303056\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3303056&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzpAoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=8abb94b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3303056&h=c7250d43\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3303056</a><br />\n<br />\n2020/09/25 16:00<br />\n〔記者楊媛婷／台北報導〕中華民國野鳥學會日前拒絕更名、拒簽承諾不促進或倡導台灣獨立文件遭國際鳥盟除名，中華鳥會今天發布聲明，決定將學會的名稱從Chinese Wild Bird Federation（CWBF）更改為 Taiwan Wild Bird Federation（TWBF）以利國際辨識。<br />\n<br />\n國際鳥盟為了進入中國的保育圈，便主張中華鳥會的「中文名稱」會帶來風險，要求中華鳥會改名，還強迫中華鳥會簽署不承認台灣本身有合法政權的離譜文件，中華鳥會拒簽後，國際鳥盟執行長甚至一度寫信給所有成員，指控中華鳥會將政治涉入保育工作。"},{"pid":"89b837862674e231549ff009052aaa0c650c7397","tid":2217207,"uid":378141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T09:25:54.000Z","msg":"抵L死 奶共後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da839daec5790d330c7921625a38d1be13a6d2ad","tid":2217207,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T09:26:35.000Z","msg":"中國人又成功爭取台灣去中國化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}